            . On the morning of the 22d of March I went to Billingsgate, and left my great coat in my cart, on <placeName id="t18240407-41-crimeloc233">St. Mary's Hill</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18240407-41-crimeloc233" type="placeName" value="St. Mary's Hill"></interp>
